                <note rend="inline" type="source">811.20 Defense (M)/47<hi rend="superscript"
                        >4/22</hi>: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Consul at Hanoi</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Reed</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1940-06-28T12:00:00-04:00"
                            >June 28, 1940—noon</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Your June 28, 10 a.m., and June 27, 7 p.m. The American Government definitely
                    purchased this wolfram and antimony and shipments are to be consigned to an
                    agency of the American Government.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hull</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
